column5: NOT SURE WHAT I WAS THINKIN WHEN I VENTURED OUT FISHIN YESTERDAY. AFTER ABOUT THE FIRST HR AND TOES GOIN NUMB I WAS FEELIN THE SUN ON MY FACE REMEMBERIN BASS FISHIN IN SHORTS IN THE BOAT. MUST BE AGE GETTIN TO ME BUT HURRY UP JUNE  LOL FRESH IN MALE ON THE FLY   FALL COLOUR MALE  NICE FRESH HEN   JUST WAITED OVER NIGHT DIDNT DO NOTHIN BUT PHOTOBUCKET SEEMS TO BE OK NOW. TX ALL FOR HELP

NOT SURE IF IT WAS WORTH FREEZING BUT SURE BEATS WORK OR SITTIN AT HOME  LOL WENT BASS FISHIN TODAY. 52INCH PLASMA AND PS3 MAY BE MY NEW FRIEND THIS WINTER  LOL NOW IF I COULD ONLY CATCH A 13LB BASS ON SCUGOG LIKE THE VIDEO GAME  LOL

You are the man and were rewarded with nice fish.  I was so close to go fishing over the weekend but got chickened out at the last minute when seeing flags flying high up in the air.  nice fish. lets pray it gets warmer now  Cheers,
